Background data on shigellosis in Armenia
-----------------------------------------
(Disease rates for Russian Federation (RF) and USA added for comparison)
Year / Armenian cases / rates per 100 000 -- rate in RF -- rate in USA
1993 / 2520 / 72.0 -- 127.7 -- 12.48
1994 / 1632 / 46.6 -- 149.0 -- 11.44
1995 / 1071 / 30.6 -- 184.7 -- 12.32
1996 / 1036 / 29.6 -- 85.3 -- 9.80
1997 / 882 / 25.2 -- 57.2 -- 8.64
1998 / 1216 / 34.7 -- 74.8 -- 8.74
1999 / 1353 / 36.6 -- 148.4 -- 6.43
2000 / 771 / 20.8 -- 123.5 -- 8.41
